WORKERS; NATIONAL TRANSPORTATION SAFETY BOARD; WITNESSES; INVESTIGATIONS; 
NEGLIGENCE; TRANSPORTATION SAFETY; HEALTH AND SAFETY VIOLATIONS; EQUIPMENT 
