<P>
NICARAGUA HOLDS 2 U.S. BOATS, CREWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
WASHINGTON 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Nicaraguan navy has seized two U.S.-owned fishing boats for lack of proper 
documentation and is detaining the vessels and their crews at the port of 
Bluefields, the State Department said Monday. 
</P>
