Carolco Pictures Inc. has sold a package of feature films to Sky Television, a 
satellite channel in the United Kingdom owned by Rupert Murdoch's News Corp. 
The first two Carolco titles to premiere on the Sky Movie Channel will be 
"Rambo: First Blood II," starring Sylvester Stallone, and "Angel Heart," 
