Gone in an Instant: Singer Paul McCartney's Nov. 27-29 concert dates at the 
Forum were near-instant sellouts Monday, so tickets were put on sale for two 
additional dates: Nov. 23 (Thanksgiving) and Nov. 24. They immediately sold 
out, too. A spokeswoman for the promoter, Parc Presentations, said no more 
dates would be added to the engagement, which will be the tour's only Southern 
California stop. McCartney's last local appearance was a three-night stand at 
the Forum in June, 1976. ALEENE MacMINN 
</P>
