</P>
<P>
2nd: $33.5 
</P>
<P>
3rd: $32.3 
</P>
<P>
4th: $28.7 
</P>
<P>
1989 
</P>
<P>
1st: $28.4 
</P>
<P>
2nd: $27.7 
</P>
<P>
Source: Commerce Department 
</P>
</TEXT>
